{"tid":1416532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"背水一戰，請團結","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:44:53.000Z","uid":110857,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e20acb628d906776b8aaa7a203a26e926ee4fa","tid":1416532,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"無論前線勇武定文宣，或者民意撚定和理非，請大家係呢一夜之後要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷靜落嚟</span></strong></span>！<br />\n<br />\n我相信無論係得呢個地方開post定係留comment都係想打贏呢場仗，打死班狗打倒林奠。所以大家一定要互相尊重各種意見！<br />\n<br />\n致前線勇武派: <br />\n<br />\n呢兩個月以嚟，如果當初無衝擊立法會，送中一早就過咗。無前線對抗d狗，死傷可能更嚴重，運動亦無可能持續兩個幾月。呢樣證明咗<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武抗爭成效好大！</span></span> 因為好多人嘅犧牲，令我地都好想打撚死哂d黑警，我相信好多人都有同感。對任何前線嘅行為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">絕對尊重</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">致以最崇高嘅敬意</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n致後援部:<br />\n<br />\n每次嘅遊行示威都總有辦法號召民眾，以人數為武器，令運動keep住個熱度。無遊行示威，就可能無辦法將運動打到兩個幾月。亦有一班有心之士知自己無能力參與前線工作，會花上可以付出嘅精力做文宣。設計poster， 印貼紙，甚至去跪地去道歉，呢d對前線係一種好大嘅支持。為參與運動嘅人去諗同宣傳當有事嘅時候可以點走，向身邊人宣揚各個運動嘅資訊等等，都絕對係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">運動當中好重要嘅一部分！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n無論你相信嘅係邊一套，呢個運動我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必須贏</span></span>！仲要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">贏得徹徹底底</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n我唔係分析時勢做軍師，亦唔係想將大家分黨分派，我只係希望大家可以從心支持對方嘅諗法。否則無可能繼續走落去。<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動之所以能夠走到呢一個關口，每個肯參與討論嘅巴絲都係成就者之一。亦都正正因為呢個原因，各位巴絲一定要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">團結一心</span></span>！做真正嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不割蓆不分化不篤灰</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n無論口號係乜都好，呢個運動係時候需要升級！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">換d新方法去玩落去</span></span>！捱得過呢個位，終點在望！"},{"pid":"1af36f219933ec93602455144dd87e6f346444ce","tid":1416532,"uid":210088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"[紅色警示] 五毛、分化撚、失敗撚、割𥱊撚 大量活躍，請冷處理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415513</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eb3e95daf1401bec27da7baceb5fb79cf4c6428e","tid":1416532,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2bdd817f7b9a12a1078d26a9d82e6b7fedcc3661","tid":1416532,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:14:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"13b321095585a452537bbcbabdba751d12ee4d37","tid":1416532,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cdb405e8cb8c3e3fa15a7583f0cbb5d5296c7b01","tid":1416532,"uid":253573,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:14:42.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n手足們 對住普通市民 要保持禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過埋今晚 全力打文宣戰！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416041</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b16b7c6550239b0296804c86d80babc00d22ff6","tid":1416532,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:14:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5715e3462431dd5f90797d6db90412e0b0cc1ae6","tid":1416532,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:15:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"413905827842d9d1d7dfc84490f4476752fc1b27","tid":1416532,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:15:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f0e31da8d76d861ea407282fe466e71fe0bddeda","tid":1416532,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:15:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"11213ea5a71625f69ef101dd9d8ce0b4d68da120","tid":1416532,"uid":110857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"